          .span4
            %img#icon{:src => "img/icon.png"}/
          #summary.span5
            %h1 Nimbus
            %p 
              Nimbus uses FUSE to bring the native file management experience to 
              %a{:href=>"http://getcloudapp.com/"}
                CloudApp.
              It allows you to sort, open, upload, delete, and Quicklook your uploaded files.
